The spatially resolved kinematics pipeline for DESJ2112 requires a combined_backup of the integrated velocity dispersion, 
which we can obtain via the integrated velocity dispersion measurements. You can either run the pipeline to get the integrated velocity dispersion,
or you can use the following drive link (https://drive.google.com/file/d/14u_GBfR1jl_kXqK3Tu63h60iSX2M7J-F/view?usp=sharing) to obtain the necessary params.
